caption: Table 1: Epochs required to reach specified errors with varying embedding sizes for 2-FGNN.
description: This table shows the number of training epochs needed to achieve a training error of 10<sup>-6</sup> and 10<sup>-12</sup> for a 2-FGNN model with different embedding sizes (64, 128, 256, 512, 1024, 2048).  It demonstrates the impact of embedding size on training efficiency, showing that larger embedding sizes initially lead to faster convergence but that the gains eventually level off.
